# Target groups & health

## Target group

The **unit of routing** — holds targets + health config, reusable across listeners / LBs. Only **healthy** targets get traffic.

## Health check

Protocol + path (e.g. `/health`) on an **interval** (30 s). **Healthy threshold** (passes → in) · **unhealthy threshold** (fails → out).

## Deregistration delay (draining)

On removal, stop **new** requests, wait for in-flight ones (default **300 s**). Lower for stateless; higher for WebSockets.

## Cross-zone load balancing

Spread evenly across **all AZs**. **ALB: on + free** · **NLB/GWLB: off** (cross-AZ transfer charges).
